This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning models and the impact of sample distribution on performance, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions clustering objects into visually similar class groups, which is a topic related to natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM).
